{"type":null,"faqId":45338,"title":"如何使用手机控制荣耀盒子M321？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{margin-left:1.18125in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{text-indent:-0.110416666in;margin-left:1.18125in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p3{margin-bottom:0.2777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.s1{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.41527778in;}\n.s2{font-weight:bold;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>请按照如下步骤操作：</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">步骤 1  </span><span>将手机和荣耀盒子M321连接至同一家庭网络。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">步骤 2  </span><span>在“</span><span class=\"s2\">设置 &gt; 网络 &gt; 网络状态</span><span>”中找到盒子的 IP 地址。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=164856\" style=\"width:4.3729167in;height:2.4631944in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">步骤 1  </span><span>扫描二维码，添加盒子微信公众号“</span><span class=\"s2\">华为荣耀盒子M321</span><span>”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=164857\" style=\"width:1.2284722in;height:1.2284722in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  >\n<span>您也可以进入盒子“</span><span class=\"s2\">应用 &gt; 帮助 &gt; 使用技巧</span><span>”，选择“</span><span class=\"s2\">创意遥控器，使用更有趣</span><span>”。查看该二维码。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">步骤 1  </span><span>在手机上打开微信公众号，选择“</span><span class=\"s2\">应用 </span><span>&gt; </span><span class=\"s2\">遥控器</span><span>”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">步骤 2  </span><span>输入盒子的 IP 地址，点击连接。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">----结束</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>此时，您将能使用微信上的遥控器控制荣耀盒子M321。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":245,"faqType":"多屏互动","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"859","faqTypeCode":"Media_Device-Screen-Sharing","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1442556874000,"seriesProductName":"MediaQ M321,MediaQ M321-20","visitedTimes":69,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"手机,控制,荣耀盒子","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}